<paragraph id="IFRS17_42" base="F55666250" principles="yes"><paranum>42</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 17"/><data name="paranum" value="42"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS17_P0154">An entity shall recognise income and expenses for the following changes in the carrying amount of the <xref base="F55667006" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0550">liability for incurred claims<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0227"/></ph></xref>: </p><ol id="IFRS17_L0028" base="F55666252" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p id="IFRS17_P0155" base="F55666253">insurance service expenses&#x2014;for the increase in the liability because of claims and expenses incurred in the period, excluding any <xref base="F55666984" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0542">investment components<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0204"/></ph></xref>;                    </p>       </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p id="IFRS17_P0156" base="F55666255">insurance service expenses&#x2014;for any subsequent changes in <xref base="F55666938" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0525">fulfilment cash flows<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0143"/></ph></xref> relating to incurred claims and incurred expenses; and</p>       </li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value>         <p id="IFRS17_P0157" base="F55666257">insurance finance income or expenses&#x2014;for the effect of the time value of money and the effect of <xref base="F55666934" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0524">financial risk<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0129"/></ph></xref> as specified in <xref id="IFRS17_X0188" base="F59119544" href="IFRS17_g87-92.dita#IFRS17_g87-92/IFRS17_g87-92_TI">paragraph 87</xref>.                    </p>       </li></ol></body></paragraph>